# ── Node ──────────────────────────────────────────────
node_modules/
npm-debug.log*

# ── Terraform ─────────────────────────────────────────
# State files contain real resource IDs and secrets (e.g. ACR passwords).
# Use a remote backend (GCS / Azure Blob) for shared state instead.
**/.terraform/
**/.terraform.lock.hcl
**/terraform.tfstate
**/terraform.tfstate.backup
**/terraform.tfstate.*.backup

# terraform.tfvars contains real project IDs / subscription IDs / secrets.
# Each developer copies terraform.tfvars.example and fills in their own values.
**/terraform.tfvars

# Crash and override files
**/crash.log
**/override.tf
**/override.tf.json
**/*_override.tf
**/*_override.tf.json

# ── Environment / secrets ─────────────────────────────
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# ── Editor ────────────────────────────────────────────
.vscode/settings.json
.idea/
*.swp
*.swo

# ── OS ────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
